General.Name: Venture Minerals
General.Description: Venture Minerals Limited engages in the mineral exploration and development business in Australia. The company explores for nickel, iron, cobalt, tin, tungsten, copper, silver, gold, lead, zinc, and PGE deposits. Its flagship project is the 100% owned Mount Lindsay project that covers an area of approximately 159 square kilometers located in north-western Tasmania. Venture Minerals Limited was incorporated in 2006 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
